parameters: A machine whirrs in the distance.
\n<\n[1]>What's this girl doing down here under the dwarf fortress?\.\. She hiding from something...?\.\.
There's a body here.\.\. At first Neneko thinks it must be some kind of unfortunate victim of that big green lizard nearby...\.\.\.
But for some reason she gets the feeling that thing wouldn't be able to hurt anything bigger than a puppy even if it wanted to,\. except by accident.\.\.
Oh yeah,\. and also she's clearly asleep,\. not dead or unconscious.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>What's this girl doing down here under the dwarf fortress?\.\. She hiding from something...?\.\.
With Neneko's luck maybe she wandered into some kinda thieves den or serial killer hideout or something...\.\.\.
The cat eyes the girl,\. sizing her up.\.\. She's rather curvy and plump,\. that's plain and clear enough from the rags she's wearing to cover herself up.\.\.
She's also pretty short and stocky.\.\. Definitely got the body of a Dwarf.\.\.
The scales and spikes,\. along with her horns,\. claws,\. and tail were definitely not something she'd seen on any other dwarves,\. though.\.\.
Right then.\.\. Neneko's summation: She could definitely take this girl if she happened to have some dark secret.\.\.
Considering how unlikely that was given this sad little hole and the derpy lizard staring off into space,\. she'll at least have the decency to not wreck this girl in her sleep.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Ah well.\.\. Hey,\. girly,\. it's rude to sleep while you have a guest over~
Neneko crouches down next to the not very lean,\. very much green,\. and probably not mean dwarf(?),\. grabbing her shoulder and giving it a shake.\.\.
In response she groans,\. turning away,\. her tail curling over herself.\.\.
\n<???>Ghkhuh...\.\.\. muff...\.\.\. Gigi,\. it's not time for lunch yet...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>It's Nene,\. not Gigi.\.\. \BST[7]And only to friends,\. missy.\.\.
\n<???>Gigi ya learned how to talk...\.\.\. das nice...\.\.\.
The dwarf(?) mumbles sleepily,\. her eyes fluttering open.\.\. Neneko sees the odd color in them,\. the sclera yellow instead of white,\. and her irises a sharp red.\.\.
Those eyes turn to look at Neneko,\. only half awake...\.\.\.
Before they shoot open,\. wide surprised orbs as the dwarf practically leaps in shock!\.\.
Neneko,\. unimpressed,\. waves a hand in greeting.\.\.
The short and stocky girl crawls backwards away from Neneko until her back hits the wall.\.\.
\n<???>What in blazes-!!\.\. An intruder!!\.\. Y-\.you!!\.\. What're you-!!\.\.
Neneko simply watches the girl panic,\. with all the interest of a bored house cat.\.\.
\n<???>How'd you even find-\. no,\. that doesn't matter!\.\. Gigi!\.\.
With a sudden burst of bravery the panic gives way to some weird kinda determination as the dwarf darts over to the large,\. slumped over lizard...\.\.\.
And spreads her arms as if shielding it from Neneko.\.\.
\n<???>You!\.\. Get out of our hideout!\.\. We got nothin' for you,\. beast girl!\.\. This Gegerro's no use to you,\. so leave 'em alone!\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Whoa now.\.\. First off,\. I already told you my name.\.\. Second off,\. yeah,\. I can definitely tell there's nothing here.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Third off,\. I don't want anything!\.\. Actually,\. I was wondering what YOU are doing down here!\.\.
The dwarf glaaares at Neneko with clear suspicion.\.\.
\n<???>...\.\.\. Well,\. I guess a cat girl sneaking through the rest of the fortress and waking me up to rob me specifically doesn't make much sense...\.\.\.
\n<Perina>...\.\.\. Name's Perina.\.\. Sorry 'bout being all jumpy like that...\.\.\.
Neneko glances at the lizard,\. humming as she looks around.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>So,\. why are you down in this dingy hobo cave,\. anyway?\.\. \BST[1]You're a dwarf,\. ain't ya?\.\.
Neneko gives a curious hum,\. pretending to think it over.\.\.
Perina snorts,\. her tail waving behind her.\.\.
\n<Perina>...\.\.\. Why do you wanna know?\.\. There's better dwarves to talk to...\.\.\. case you haven't noticed I'm kind of an outcast...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Blame my curiosity.\.\. \BST[1,Neneko2]It's one of my cutest and most charming features.\.\.
\n<Perina>...\.\.\. I guess a beast girl wouldn't really get it,\. but if you haven't noticed,\. I'm not exactly a 'normal' dwarf.\.\.
She sighs,\. holding up a claw,\. staring at it.\.\.
\n<Perina>I'm a "mutant".\.\. These lizard parts make me stand out...\.\.\.
Perina looks unimpressed.\.\. She shudders,\. looking up at the ceiling.\.\.
\n<Perina>You prolly already know that the dwarves have a...\.\.\. territory problem with the kobolds.\.\.
\n<Perina>Well.\.\. With all the other dwarves being so jumpy,\. I really don't want to run around sporting scales and a big tail like this.\.\.
\n<Perina>I'd probably get run through before I can even say I'm one of them...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>How come ya don't leave,\. then?\.\. It'd probably be better than,\. you know,\. living right underneath them.\.\.
She looks at the large,\. slumped over lizard.\.\. Neneko catches where her eyes are looking and moves over,\. crouching beside her.\.\.
\n<Perina>...\.\.\. I've planned on sneaking out at night,\. but with him like this...\.\.\.
\n<Perina>He got injured a while ago...\.\.\. probably sick,\. too.\.\. I've been trying to take care of him but...\.\.\.
\n<Perina>Sigh ...\.\.\. A full grown Gegerro is a lot harder to feed than a single dwarf.\.\. I can't sneak in and out of here to get the food I need for both of us.\.\.
\n<Perina>We're barely getting by,\. and he's not getting any better.\.\.
Perina looks to Neneko,\. frowning,\. her red eyes glistening with determination.\.\.
\n<Perina>He's my best friend.\.\. I...\.\.\. \BST[1]I've raised him since he was a little egg,\. y'know?\.\.

\n<Perina>Ever since this all started,\. I've been hiding down here with Gigi...\.\.\. I wanna get out of here,\. but I ain't leaving him behind,\. but I can't get the stuff I need to make her better...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>So I can help,\. duh?\.\. Why else would I ask?\.\.
\n<Perina>...\.\.\. Cuz you ask a lot of invasive questions.\.\.
Neneko glares at the dwarf,\. who pointedly looks away.\.\.
\n<Perina>...\.\.\. I won't tell you unless you tell me why you want to help.\.\. I don't got any reward for you.\.\.
Neneko grins,\. reaching over to gently pat the Gegerro.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Honestly,\. I like animals more than people.\.\. They don't piss you off or act all high and mighty around you.\.\. \BST[1,Neneko2]Just give 'em food and they'll mind their business.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>So seeing this big cutie be so weak and sad rubs me the wrong way.\.\.
She huffs,\. standing up and turning to Perina.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>In other words,\. I'm doing this for Gigi,\. not you.\.\. \BST[7]That enough for ya?\.\.
Perina stares up at Neneko in disbelief.\.\.
\n<Perina>But...\.\.\. but if you really want to help,\. then...\.\.\. I'd really appreciate it.\.\.
\n<Perina>Right now what I think Gigi really needs is food.\.\. He's barely gotten anything but scraps since he became an adult.\.\.
\n<Perina>If he just had more energy I think he'd start getting better right away.\.\. \BST[1]Gegerro are sturdy like that.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Food!\.\. Easy enough.\.\. What does a Gegerro eat?\.\.
\n<Perina>Um...\.\.\. if you can,\. bring a couple of \ii[169].\.\. Maybe 3 or so for now.\.\. It's his favorite food.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Sounds gross...\.\.\. \BST[5]but hey,\. I'm no lizard gourmet.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Alright,\. time to go make a food run!\.\. Don't miss me too much,\. Gigi!\.\.
\n<Perina>...\.\.\. Focus on Gigi for now.\.\. I can take care of myself.\.\.
It's some kind of humongous lizard with a rather cute and innocent dumb face.\.\. It doesn't seem to react when you poke it,\. though.\.\. It looked rather sluggish and weak...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>This thing looks like it ain't feeling too hot...\.\.\. \BST[2]what's wrong,\. big guy?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>You hear that,\. Gigi?\.\. We got something special for ya~
The derpy big lizard tilts his head.\.\. Neneko doubts he actually understood anything at all,\. but it did look damn cute doing that.\.\.
Probably smelled his favorite snack,\. too.\.\.
Neneko grins,\. stepping over.\.\. Perina follows behind,\. looking hopeful.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Or maybe dinner?\.\. \BST[5,Neneko]I unno,\. can't really tell what time it is down here.\.\. Anyway,\. here,\. try one of these.\.\. They're...\.\.\. fresh?\.\. I think?\.\.
Neneko takes hold of one of the \ii[169]s,\. weighing it in her hand before holding it up towards the Gegerro.\.\.
The Gegerro's eyes sloooowly turn towards the treat,\. but it doesn't move,\. its body rumbling in a low,\. lazy,\. weak hiss.\.\.
Neneko frowns,\. holding the treat closer,\. waving it in front of Gigi's eyes and dangling it close to its mouth.\.\.
In response,\. Gigi slowly raises his head and bumps his nose against Neneko's hand before dropping back down to rest.\.\.
Neneko frowns,\. holding the treat closer,\. waving it in front of Gigi's eyes and dangling it close to its mouth.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Don't tell me I got them spoiled...\.\.\.
Neneko sniffs the \ii[169] in her hand,\. then winces and makes a face of disgust.\.\.
\n<Perina>Don't worry.\.\. That's how it's supposed to smell.\.\.
The dwarf then sighs,\. looking at Gigi in worry.\.\.
\n<Perina>He must be weaker than I thought...\.\.\. oh Gigi,\. you're too pooped to even eat,\. aren't you?\.\. Come on,\. just a bite...\.\.\.
Perina tries to nudge Gigi to move towards his meal,\. whispering little encouragements and petting him.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Tsk...\.\.\. this is bad,\. isn't it?\.\. What now...?\.\. Even if we force one of these into his mouth he probably won't even chew.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>We gotta force him to eat,\. but if we just shove 'em in he'll choke.\.\.
The cat eyes the \ii[169] in her hand.\.\. It was time to think.\.\. How to feed these to Gigi when he won't even chew?\.\.
Neneko shuddered as an idea came to her.\.\. It could work,\. but...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Okay,\. so if he won't chew his food...\.\.\. wh-\.what if...\.\.\.
She eyes the Roll.\.\. It looked very...\.\.\. firm.\.\.
Chew the \ii[169] and feed it to Gigi yourself. For the good boy!
No no no no no no no absolutely NOT.
Chew the \ii[169] and feed it to Gigi yourself. For the good boy!
The cat quivers in fear,\. gripping the \ii[169] firmly in her hand.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Just pretend you're biting on a really thick and gooey chicken...\.\.\. that you're going to spit into a giant lizard's mouth...\.\.\.
Her tail jitters nervously as she tries to pump herself up for what she was about to do.\.\. The sacrifice she was about to make for this cute big green baby.\.\.
She opens her mouth,\. slowly bringing the head of the \ii[169] closer...\.\.\.
Only for the \ii[169] to get swiped out of her hand!\.\.
She looks over and sees Perina,\. taking the \ii[169] wordlessly.\.\.
She bites down on the \ii[169],\. taking a huge chunk out of it.\.\.
Neneko fights back the urge to gag.\.\.
No no no no no no no absolutely NOT.
Neneko retches and holds the \ii[169] far away from her face.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Nope.\.\. No way.\.\. Can't.\.\. Too...\.\.\. too much.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Honestly,\. who'd ever do something so gross.\.\. No thanks.\.\. \BST[7]Only someone crazy would put one of these in their mouth.\.\.
Neneko huffs.\.\. It was time to go back to the drawing board.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Maybe cutting it up into a buncha little pieces...\.\.\. or mashing it into paste or something...\.\.\.
As she ran some ideas in her head,\. however...\.\.\.
Perina suddenly swipes the \ii[169]s from her!\.\.
The dwarf ignores her,\. however,\. eying one of the Rolls for a long moment.\.\.
And chomps right into it,\. taking a huge chunk out of it!\.\.
Perina closes her eyes,\. chewing thoroughly,\. her cheeks puffing out as she takes another bite out of the \ii[169].\.\.
Gigi lifts his head,\. rumbling lowly as he turns his gaze to Perina.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Ehh...\.\.\. \BST[5]he's reacting...\.\.\. maybe he smells the Rolls now?\.\.
Neneko watches as the Gegerro lazily lumbers over to the dwarflizard and practically topples her over as his entire weight is thrown on top of her.\.\.
The dwarf waves a claw,\. then grabs the Gegerro's face,\. pushing his mouth open.\.\.
Neneko watches in horrid fascination as she feeds Gigi,\. like a mama bird to her chicks.\.\.
\n<Perina>...\.\.\. It didn't taste that bad...\.\.\. \BST[1]but maybe it's the lizard in me...\.\.\.
Gigi nudges against Perina,\. making some sort of huge derpy lizard equivalent of a purr.\.\.
\n<Perina>Finally getting some energy back,\. aren't you...?\.\. There's more,\. don't worry...\.\.\.
The dwarf is rather gentle and extremely doting suddenly.\.\. She doesn't even really think about biting into more of the \ii[169] and chewing it up.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Looks like things are gonna be fine now!\.\.
\n<Perina>Mmh.\.\. Thanks a lot,\. Neneko.\.\. Had my doubts,\. but...\.\.\. I'm sure Gigi's grateful too.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Hey,\. like I said,\. I did it for him!\.\.
\n<Perina>...\.\.\. Either way,\. you don't have to stick around if you don't want to...\.\.\. Once Gigi's recovered,\. we're leaving.\.\.
\n<Perina>...\.\.\. We're pretty independent and capable,\. even if we don't look it.\.\.
As Perina says this,\. Gigi has practically flopped right on her,\. demanding more food and attention.\.\.
\n<Perina>Mff.\.\. We can get out on our own.\.\. I'm gonna move somewhere we might be accepted more...\.\.\. and somewhere Gigi can be comfy and spoiled all he likes.\.\.
\n<Perina>I will...\.\.\. we will...\.\.\. surely find a way to thank you,\. Neneko...
\n<\n[1]>Hah...\.\.\. well,\. if you're sure.\.\. \BST[5]Good luck with that,\. Peri.\.\.
Perina waves her claw in farewell.\.\. Neneko flicks her tail and waves back,\. suppressing a shudder as the dwarf goes back to...\.\.\. feeding.\.\.
Well,\. at least she could say she did her good deed for the day.\.\. Even if her appetite's totally gone now.\.\.
Neneko pets Gigi affectionately.\.\. She had to admit,\. this big tough lizard skin is kind of addicting to touch.\.\.
"\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>We two dear dwarves, friends forever, were here. If you want to know our names, they are Reg and Zasit!\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]"
